headline: American Express Renews Support for Local Restaurants with 2025 Grant Program
summary: American Express today announced the return of its Backing International Small Restaurants grant program in Canada, reaffirming its commitment to helping small, independent restaurants grow and thrive. In partnership with the International Downtown Association (IDA) Foundation, the 2025 program will offer 20 grants of $20,000 CAD each to selected restaurants in Toronto and Montreal.
